desc_short	-----								VirZOOM creates thrilling Virtual Reality experiences powered by you. Pedal your VirZOOM controller to propel yourself through endlessly exciting VR games. Power a horse in a race, a tank in battle, a fire-breathing dragon through mountains. A workout without the work.							
